{{Expand German|topic=culture|date=July 2011|America – The Freedom to Be}} {{Infobox television | show_name = America – The Freedom to Be | show_name_2 = USA & Canada - The freedom to be... | image = | caption = | camera = | runtime = | creator = | starring = | country = [[Germany]] | network = [[Westdeutscher Rundfunk|WDR]] | first_aired = | last_aired = | num_seasons = 1 | num_episodes = 13 | list_episodes = }}
'''''America – The Freedom to Be''''' was a thirteen-part German educational television series teaching the [[English language]] with an [[United States|American]] and [[Canada|Canadian]] theme. Produced by [[Westdeutscher Rundfunk|WDR]], the program is an extension of its ''[[Fast Track English]]'' series.
